implements WindowsLocalService

An implementation of the model object 'Windows Local Service'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Dependant Components
  • Error Control
  • Executable Path
  • Log On As System
  • Run Program
  • Service Account
  • Service Account Password
  • Service Dependencies
  • Service Description
  • Service Display Name
  • Service Name
  • Service Status
  • Start Params
  • Startup Type
